          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Used to compute your basal metabolic rate.",
          "target": "用于计算您的基础代谢率。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Used in the standard sex-specific basal metabolic rate estimate. Pick whichever fits you best, or choose non-binary or prefer not to say to use the average of the two.",
          "target": "用于标准的性别特异性基础代谢率估算。请选择最符合您情况的选项，或选择非二元/不愿透露以使用两者的平均值。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Used to estimate your total daily energy expenditure.",
          "target": "用于估算您的每日总能量消耗。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Optional fallback used for body mass index and nutrition recommendations when you haven't logged a body weight in a workout yet. Logged weights from workout blocks always take precedence, so once you start logging this value is ignored.",
          "target": "当您尚未在锻炼中记录体重时，用于身体质量指数和营养建议的可选后备值。来自锻炼区块的记录体重始终优先，因此一旦您开始记录，此值将被忽略。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Pick whichever best matches what you're working toward right now. You can switch any time.",
          "target": "请选择最符合您当前目标的选项。您可以随时切换。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "One folder per line. Subfolders are included automatically, so listing `Cooking` covers `Cooking/Dinner`, `Cooking/Breakfast`, etc. Each recipe should have `calories`, `protein`, `carbs`, and `fats` in its frontmatter, per serving.",
          "target": "每行一个文件夹。子文件夹会自动包含，因此列出 `Cooking` 会覆盖 `Cooking/Dinner`、`Cooking/Breakfast` 等。每个食谱的 frontmatter 中应包含每份的 `calories`、`protein`、`carbs` 和 `fats`。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Show fiber as a 5th macro in the meal log, recipe parsing, and analytics. Off by default. Useful if you're tracking fiber for diabetic-friendly meal planning or general gut health.",
          "target": "在餐食记录、食谱解析和分析中将纤维显示为第五种宏量营养素。默认关闭。如果您正在为糖尿病友好型膳食规划或一般肠道健康追踪纤维，此功能很有用。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Targets shown as progress bars in the meal log block.",
          "target": "在餐食记录区块中以进度条形式显示的目标。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Used when displaying and logging weights.",
          "target": "用于显示和记录体重。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Optional target weight in your selected unit. Shown in the body weight analytics section as a target line and gap-to-goal stat. Leave blank to disable.",
          "target": "您所选单位中的可选目标体重。在体重分析部分显示为目标线和差距统计。留空则禁用。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Lets you append extra sets to an exercise mid-workout. Off by default since most lifters stick to the planned set count.",
          "target": "允许您在锻炼过程中向运动添加额外组数。默认关闭，因为大多数举重者会坚持计划的组数。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Length of the break timer in seconds (30 to 300).",
          "target": "休息计时器的时长（秒）（30 到 300）。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Shorter pause between exercises within a superset (10–120 seconds). The full default duration still applies once you complete a round of all paired exercises.",
          "target": "超级组内运动之间的较短暂停（10-120 秒）。完成一轮所有配对运动后，仍会应用完整的默认时长。"
